{
  "2367610": {
    "name": "Critter Café",
    "steam_appid": 2367610,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/bcf0f948ea6be70edaba7476eef5c23b.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=125 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/dfbbd142baf0db4945fb03e467407f10.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造你自己的舒适咖啡馆，打造出一个温馨的空间，让镇民可在此相聚，并与来到咖啡馆的可爱小生物们共度时光！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/5eb74130606fe79e80a8960990c2cea3.poster.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/5eb74130606fe79e80a8960990c2cea3.webm?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/5eb74130606fe79e80a8960990c2cea3.mp4?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/e83d6cf0720ddef96663077affde301d.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=125 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >画出完美的拿铁拉花、呈上蛋糕并端上咖啡，而满心期待与咖啡馆中小生物共度时光的客人们也会蜂拥而来。举办以小生物为主题的派对：电影之夜、生日宴会，以及更多其他活动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/8646f87f6dae54f5de09c5d5ac809ef5.poster.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/8646f87f6dae54f5de09c5d5ac809ef5.webm?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/8646f87f6dae54f5de09c5d5ac809ef5.mp4?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/eec88a9c31f562607bc6348b35c1cc0d.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=125 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你探索Otherlands这个魔幻世界的同时，发掘并拯救35种可爱小生物！找出Mogbert、Glowli，以及更多其他等着与你相会的超可爱生物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/1ead1ac43abd96b713e2242ff5cc6d42.poster.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/1ead1ac43abd96b713e2242ff5cc6d42.webm?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/1ead1ac43abd96b713e2242ff5cc6d42.mp4?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/3af20f129210821a4650e0ef5cbd8c06.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=125 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心关爱、照料你的小生物：你可以与它们一起玩、喂它们吃各种点心、帮它们洗澡和梳毛。小生物和你一起进行咖啡馆的各种活动时，也会逐渐与你建立羁绊、发展出新的特性，并解锁可爱的新外观！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/857a9d671aebf766dd7c5347b96598fe.poster.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/857a9d671aebf766dd7c5347b96598fe.webm?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/857a9d671aebf766dd7c5347b96598fe.mp4?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/c3d125a173f3258c20bb4128d7b716f2.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=125 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你收到许多神秘的来信，信上提到Gold Leaf Isle各处都出现了魔法传送门。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索多个令人兴奋的地点和生机盎然的世界。穿过传送门进入Otherlands，通过谜题的考验，并寻找新的小生物，好好照顾它们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/ec3ebafb18b096dafd25b2d80bceb62d.poster.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/ec3ebafb18b096dafd25b2d80bceb62d.webm?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/ec3ebafb18b096dafd25b2d80bceb62d.mp4?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/8913812e33a0fa2d1cfb80f96ad7aff7.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=125 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情表达自我！用各式各样的外观自定义你的角色，随时都能加以调整。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花点时间设计咖啡馆的各种细节，包括桌子、椅子、沙发、壁纸、地板、墙壁装饰等更多内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救小生物后，你也能自定义它们的栖地，让它们能在新家里面快乐生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/4c212746aa666778343d674183d1ee51.poster.avif?t=1766419951\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/4c212746aa666778343d674183d1ee51.webm?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367610/extras/4c212746aa666778343d674183d1ee51.mp4?t=1766419951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
